2026-03-22T15:45:26.246Z JOY-0026 comment.added "Plan: (1) Create joy-core::embedded module with EmbeddedFile struct (source content, target relative path, executable flag) and two functions: diff_files() returns Vec of (path, status) and sync_files() writes changed files and returns Vec of (path, action). Both use SHA-256 comparison. (2) Move commit-msg hook to data/hooks/commit-msg, reference via include_str! in the registry. (3) Define two registries: HOOK_FILES and AI_FILES as const arrays of EmbeddedFile. (4) Refactor ai.rs to use sync_files/diff_files from core instead of its own diff_templates/sync logic. (5) Refactor init.rs onboard() to use sync_files from core. (6) Remove sha2 dependency from joy-cli, add to joy-core." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
